{"type":"message","id":"f71dbb33","parentId":"b68bded0","timestamp":"2026-04-01T11:35:05.533Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. I've completed the autonomous learning task:\n1. Checked for active sessions - none found (only the cron job itself)\n2. Searched for latest industry news on all 4 topics\n3. Compiled 5 key insights into the learning notes file\n\nThe file has been saved to /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md","thinkingSignature":"dc235335e471b44823582b980a058d7c98727ee8250d6214d2ec7c61f076d9a8"},{"type":"text","text":"自主学习已完成。\n\n**执行摘要**：\n- ✅ 无活跃用户对话（仅cron任务自身）\n- ✅ 完成4个方向搜索：企业数字化转型政策 / 智能安防 / IT运维服务 / 网络系统集成\n- ✅ 整理5条关键信息，保存至 `memory/学习笔记.md`\n\n**核心学习成果**：\n1. **政策红利**：2026年中小企业数字化转型最高补贴30%，制造业转型全面攻坚\n2. **安防升级**：AI大模型+主动检测成为核心竞争力，中国市场年增长15.1%\n3. **运维变革**：AIOps进入深水区，\"人头租赁\"模式加速淘汰，效果付费成新方向\n4. **集成机遇**：网络系统集成2026-2030年CAGR 18.5%，零信任成政企刚需\n5. **道简行动建议**：AI能力建设是穿越周期的关键路径"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5852,"output":265,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50098,"cost":{"input":0.0017556,"output":0.000318,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00339303}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775043297925}}
